xZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=53e5e34a\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170220/00180_008.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 東歐國家黑山的警方在去年大選前夕阻止了刺殺時任總理久卡諾維奇的行動，惟英國傳媒引述政府消息指，刺殺事件是由俄羅斯策劃，以阻止久卡諾維奇領導的執政聯盟繼續向西方靠攏，加入北約。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170220/00180_009.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170220%2F00180_009.html&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=52404afc\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170220/00180_009.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 伊拉克總理阿巴迪宣佈政府軍將對摩蘇爾的「伊斯蘭國」（ISIS）展開新一輪攻擊，希望奪回摩蘇爾西部。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170220/s00014/1487528297313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170220%2Fs00014%2F1487528297313&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=738433b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170220%2Fs00014%2F1487528297313&h=65e68a26\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170220/s00014/1487528297313</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170220/00180_020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170220%2F00180_020.html&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1acfc8da\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170220/00180_020.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1552371&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1552371%26target%3D2&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6c89a2d9\" data-ef-